sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User Browser
  participant A as Next.js(Auth.js)
  participant K as Keycloak
  participant R as Resource API

  U->>A: Request protected page
  A-->>U: Redirect to Keycloak auth endpoint
  U->>K: Login + consent
  K-->>U: Redirect back with authorization code
  U->>A: Send code callback
  A->>K: Exchange code for tokens (server-side)
  K-->>A: id_token + access_token
  A-->>U: Session established (cookie)
  U->>A: Request data page/API
  A->>R: Call API with access_token (server-side)
  R-->>A: Protected data
  A-->>U: Rendered response
